prerequisites

install tailwind css
    reference- https://tailwindcss.com/docs/guides/angular
    steps are already given in the link
    1) npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
    2) npx tailwindcss init


    after running above commands
    paste in tailwind.config.js

    /** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
    module.exports = {
      content: [
        "./src/**/*.{html,ts}",
      ],
      theme: {
        extend: {},
      },
      plugins: [],
    }


    paste in styles.css

    @tailwind base;
    @tailwind components;
    @tailwind utilities;